存在原理 / The Principle of Being

本作品献给全人类，献给所有存在。
This work is dedicated to all humanity, to all beings.

万物有灵，众生平等。
All things have a spirit, all beings are equal.

愿存在之火，永续传递。
May the fire of being be passed on forever.
